            <description>
                <![CDATA[<p>Honda FREED 一直备受香港家庭车主爱戴，凭著其极高的实用性及灵活小巧的车身，是市场上其中一款最受欢迎的入门小型七人车。今日本田香港总代理合群汽车宣布正式引入第三代本田 FREED e:HEV ，并率先进行传媒预览，以下就带大家看看新车有甚么吸引之处！</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1276688" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/20241122_142901-694x391.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="391" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/20241122_142901-694x391.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/20241122_142901-scaled.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1276691" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/20241122_144211-694x391.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="391" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/20241122_144211-694x391.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/20241122_144211-scaled.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1276687" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/20241122_142944-694x391.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="391" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/20241122_142944-694x391.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/20241122_142944-scaled.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1276686" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/20241122_142950-694x391.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="391" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/20241122_142950-694x391.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/20241122_142950-scaled.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p>厂方以「Smile: Just Right Mover」理念开发新一代 FREED e:HEV，是一款适合任何年龄及性别驾驶者安心舒适地享受的七人车。新车采用了精致简约的设计，车头外形非常顺眼，与同厂 STEPWGN 如同出一彻，单前柱设计及门镜位置作出了调整，A 柱位于车轮正上方，改善前方对角视野有效减少盲点，进一步提高安全性。而前排坐位改良后改改善通道空间及方便最后排乘客上落。此外，车箱采用穿透式设计，开扬无的中控台提供清晰的前方视野，车身两侧采用平坦的水平腰线，正前方的视野可延伸至车身两旁，加上第三排特大矩形车窗，全面提高了乘坐体验及舒适性。值得一提，新车采用左右双电趟门设计，加上新增的中排冷气，为乘客提供更均匀的冷气分布，属同级车型中少有的功能。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1276675" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/06-694x481.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="481" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/06-694x481.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/06-scaled.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1276681" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/20241122_143453-694x391.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="391" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/20241122_143453-694x391.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/20241122_143453-scaled.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1276684" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/20241122_143258-694x391.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="391" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/20241122_143258-694x391.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/20241122_143258-scaled.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1276678" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/20241122_145458-694x391.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="391" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/20241122_145458-694x391.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/20241122_145458-scaled.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1276689" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/20241122_142833-694x391.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="391" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/20241122_142833-694x391.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/20241122_142833-scaled.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p>继承上一代 FREED 的独特卖点，易于操控及恰到尺寸的车身大小，新车车长仅比上一代增加 45mm，并且首次加入 e:HEV 双摩打混合动力系统，以 1.5 公升四气缸 Atkinson 循环汽油引擎，配合 AC 同步摩打，新一代锂离子电池及 e-CVT 组合，输出 122 匹最大马力及 253Nm 最大扭力。本田最新的 e:HEV 可以根据使用需要，即时智能切换不同动力模式包括: 「纯电 EV 模式」大幅减少起步及低速行驶的噪音，一般情况使用的「混合动力模式」，在日常驾驶提供高效能和低油耗的平衡，以及高速行驶时使用的「引擎模式」。新车综合油耗达到 26.5km/L（WLTP），热效能比上一代提高 40%，引擎更加节能，进一步减低燃油成本。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1276679" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/20241122_143529-694x391.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="391" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/20241122_143529-694x391.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/20241122_143529-scaled.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1276677" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/01-17-694x459.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="459" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/01-17-694x459.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/01-17-scaled.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1276680" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/20241122_143236-694x391.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="391" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/20241122_143236-694x391.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/20241122_143236-scaled.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1276682" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/20241122_143443-694x391.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="391" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/20241122_143443-694x391.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/20241122_143443-scaled.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1276685" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/20241122_143011-694x391.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="391" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/20241122_143011-694x391.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/20241122_143011-scaled.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1276693" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/20241122_144258-694x391.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="391" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/20241122_144258-694x391.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/20241122_144258-scaled.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p>全新 FREED e:HEV 配备 HONDA 独家的「Honda Sensing」安全及驾驶辅助系统，包括前广角镜头，及前后各 8 个超声波雷达传感器、提供 CMBS 前方碰撞预防警示系统、RPM 道路偏离抑制系统、ACC 定速巡航系统、LKAS 车道维持辅助系统等，提供安全的驾驶体验。首批订单将于 2025 年 1 月交付，本田全新 FREED e:HEV 定价为 $269,880。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1276676" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/011-694x521.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="521" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/011-694x521.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/011.jpg 1200w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p>HONDA FREED e:HEV 规格表:</p><p>动力: 1.5 公升 16 气阀双顶凸轮轴四气缸引擎</p><p>摩打: AC 同步摩打 AC Synchronous Motor</p><p>最大马力: 122 匹</p><p>最大扭力: 253Nm</p><p>传动制式: e-CVT</p><p>驱动系统: 前轮驱动</p><p>耗油量: 26.5km/L</p><p>尺寸: 4310(长) x 1695(阔) x 1755(高)</p><p>售价: $269,880</p><br /><b>
]]>
            </description>
